The '''Rivers of Stone''' was actually a cavern located on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]] where [[Barukka]] lived. Its name came from the fact that the stones took on a flowing rivers like appearance.<ref name="Courtship">''[[The Courtship of Princess Leia]]''</ref>

